bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Aug 20th 4:18 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[2.50]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>lets see, the heal song at lvl 19 heals 5hp per tic without instrument, with insturment it's 10hp a tic oh and thats both sitting down so downtime, if I twist it in battle just standing back with lute equipped it's 9hp a tic which seems to hardly help, I wonder if the heal song stacks with more bards in the group (I doubt it) I thought anthem would stack but it doesn't, hardly any of the under lvl 20 songs stack from what I have experienced, do any songs stack with multiple bards?&nbsp;&nbsp;I would like to thank everyone who contributes their knowledge on bards, it has been very helpful, I appreciate it very much, thanks =-)<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
